Uses of Package
ensg.tsi.majortom

  • Classes in ensg.tsi.majortom used by ensg.tsi.majortom 
    Class and Description
    CheckPoint
    Class for check points, points whose field coordinates are known, used to verify the accuracy after the transformation.
    Context
    Class to define the context of the georeferencer
    ControlPoint
    Class for control points, points whose field coordinates are known, used to determine the parameters of the transformation.
    Georeferencer
    Abstract class for all types of georeferencer (points, lines, polygons).
    Parameters
    Interface to define all common methods for different types of parameters
    PointConnu
    Abstract class for known points (control points and check points).
    ShapefileWriter
    Abstract class for writing shapefiles : implemented by points, lines and polygons writers.
    Transformation
    Abstract class for any type of transformation.
    TransformationFactory
    A factory of transformation, to initialize concrete transformations according to the chosen type.
    TypeTransfo
    Enumeration of available transformation types
